if\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n1.巴打你會唔會去ecuador同colombia?<br />\n2. 你係帶少少錢去先，之後遲d喺atm再攞定係一次過帶哂？平時點樣 keep住d錢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  同埋你呢個trip budget 預幾多？<br />\n<br />\nthanks"},{"pid":"20a86ac372465c90eea2c5c30d260965c862d32e","tid":157652,"uid":75637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T16:29:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>想問幾個問題：<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n1.巴打你會唔會去ecuador同colombia?<br />\n2. 你係帶少少錢去先，之後遲d喺atm再攞定係一次過帶哂？平時點樣 keep住d錢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  同埋你呢個trip budget 預幾多？<br />\n<br />\nthanks</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n呀仲有，有咩原因令你有衝動想去半年旅行？係厭倦返工生活就辭職去？<br />\n<br />\n我都想好似你咁去南美長旅行，但辭職去，冇左份工好似冇咩安全感<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ab412583eef6125b7cd87a569ec82a85989f777","tid":157652,"uid":81106,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T17:14:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>有冇諗住去玻利維亞？<br />\n<br />\n想係布宜諾斯艾利斯度搞玻利維亞簽證點睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n當地有冇去天空之鏡既團？</blockquote><br />\n有諗住, 我都仲未搞簽證<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有團, 我諗住去四日三夜由智利北邊antacrma dessert 上嗰種<br />\nbuenos aires 搞ok 呀</blockquote><br />\n有冇諗住打針，有D人話唔Check<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實atacama 出發既，3日2夜就到，除非你返智利，咁就4日3夜 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85fc021acb12194459ed0c2d9f65005a70b77492","tid":157652,"uid":40518,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T00:50:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>有冇諗住去玻利維亞？<br />\n<br />\n想係布宜諾斯艾利斯度搞玻利維亞簽證點睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n當地有冇去天空之鏡既團？</blockquote><br />\n有諗住, 我都仲未搞簽證<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有團, 我諗住去四日三夜由智利北邊antacrma dessert 上嗰種<br />\nbuenos aires 搞ok 呀</blockquote><br />\n有冇諗住打針，有D人話唔Check<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n要打黄熱, visa 講明要有, 得衛生署有, 要預約"}]}